parameters: Murasaki: H-Hey, I've been waiting for you...

Murasaki: Well then, let me explain the City
Conquest Operation, ehehe.
Sakura: Ah, please, I'm begging you.

Rurika: Hehe, nice to meet you. Please take care
of me.

Murasaki: To put it simply, we're going to take
over the central computer of the city.
Murasaki: I'll skip the details.

Murasaki: We will treat the city's operating
program as a kind of virtual reality and
infiltrate you all inside.

Murasaki: If we can break through the defense
system and reach the deepest part, it'll be okay.

Murasaki: Inside the system, be careful of the
'\C[4]\I[10]virus\C[0]'. It's a troublesome status
ailment that reduces both HP and SP at the same
time.

Murasaki: I've prepared the release item and
general skills at the shop. Will you buy them as
needed?

Murasaki: So, for the infiltration, we'll use that
machine over there.
Sakura: I see, well, it's just like usual then.

Rurika: The place we're infiltrating and the
method are just a little different, aren't they?

Kimohiko: Oh, we're going inside the computer,
huh?
Kimohiko: That sounds interesting, can I come too?

Sakura: Of course it's a no-no, my dear master
\I[15]. Just wait, because we will offer up the
city to you \I[15].

Rurika: I have a collection of onaholes for your
entertainment, Master \I[15]. Please have fun with
them over there... \I[15]
Kimohiko: Yes, understood!

Murasaki: S-So that's how it is, \I[15] let's wait
together with Onee-san and Mama, okay? \I[15]

Murasaki: Ehehe, o-of course, it's okay to play
with Mama \I[15]
Kimohiko: Have a good day!
This is...
Hey, wanna see that?

Kimohiko: Onee-chan, you had videos, right? Since
I had the chance, I tried filming Mama's too~♪
Sakura: ...Oh, really?
Rurika: ...hehe\I[15]

Sakura: You're amazing, as expected of my master
\I[15].
Rurika: Yes, it was exciting \I[15].

The hidden event Genius Mama is Son-kun's
exclusive breast onahole \I[15] has been unlocked.

Murasaki: It is possible to infiltrate the central
computer with that machine over there.
Murasaki: Just be careful, okay?
